cs.NE, cs.CE, cs.OH, cs.AI, cs.LG 

This paper discusses benchmarking of Evolutionary Algorithms for constrained optimization problems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Other likely categories include cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science), cs.OH (Other Computer Science), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
